1
00:11:58,368 --> 00:12:04,884
with these sacks of coal.
Do you understand what I'm saying?

2
00:12:04,954 --> 00:12:08,072
I didn't know who they were going to send.

3
00:12:08,141 --> 00:12:11,684
I didn't know
they were going to send eggplants.

4
00:12:11,753 --> 00:12:15,720
It's an Italian's job. Disgraceful!

5
00:14:32,915 --> 00:14:40,635
-Mr Big Shot. Spend, spend, spend.
-Enough, Pop.

6
00:14:40,707 --> 00:14:45,949
The floor was mouldy. We had to change it.

7
00:43:46,352 --> 00:43:50,601
He who arrives late has no bed!

8
00:51:22,063 --> 00:51:28,580
-Everything okay?
-Yes. Everything is fine.

9
00:51:28,650 --> 00:51:34,388
Good. We'll meet you
at the hotel in Pittsburgh.

10
00:51:34,458 --> 00:51:40,196
Make a reservation for dinner.
We'll rehearse immediately after.

11
02:09:58,123 --> 02:10:03,647
-Who's the eggplant?
-I'm working for him.

12
02:10:03,718 --> 02:10:08,322
What happened? You lose a bet?

13
02:10:12,571 --> 02:10:15,971
What the hell ya doing?

14
02:10:16,042 --> 02:10:23,125
You need work, you come to me!
I'll find you work.

15
02:10:23,197 --> 02:10:27,941
Matter of fact, I can use you this week.

16
02:10:29,784 --> 02:10:35,308
-You'll make some real money.
-A sack of money.

17
02:10:37,078 --> 02:10:43,240
-I'm already making money.
-I'll double it.

18
02:10:46,499 --> 02:10:50,819
This isn't the right place
to talk about it.

19
02:10:56,698 --> 02:11:02,151
Meet me in the bar at eight o'clock sharp.
Understand?

20
02:11:02,223 --> 02:11:08,455
-Okay, I'll see you later.
-Forget this guy.

21
02:12:52,928 --> 02:12:56,399
With you friend Dominic?

22
02:13:00,152 --> 02:13:04,047
Before accepting his offer,

23
02:13:05,535 --> 02:13:08,510
we need to talk.

